# Tank RTS To Do List

## Unit
  - Needs to have a type enum. Possible types can be: NONE = 0, ALLY = 1, ENEMY = 2
  - Must be selectable and deselectable

## Unit Selection
  - Be able to select an deselect single or multiple friendly tanks.
  - Ability to "ctrl + click" to deselect single units from a list of selected friendly tanks.

## Unit AI
  - Must be able to pathfind around obstacle to get to destination.
  - Aware of dynamic objects such as other tanks, etc.
  - Support formations
  - Have a command tank which when selected shows a menu which contents such as: a formations sub menu which can be set and all tanks in that are part of that platoon will try and maintain.
  